(3) Implant materials: titanium (Ti6Al4V — strong, biocompatible, lower modulus to reduce stress shielding), cobalt-chrome (wear surface), zirconia ceramic (low wear, brittle), UHMWPE polyethylene (bearing surface), highly crosslinked polyethylene (reduced wear);

