ตัวเลือก B (รายละเอียด)

Acute Achilles Tendon Rupture (active middle-aged athlete):

(1) either operative or non-operative — modern evidence (Willits + recent meta-analyses) shows similar re-rupture rate (~4-5%) ถ้า functional rehabilitation + early weight-bearing protocol;

(2) non-operative (functional rehab): equinus cast/boot 2 weeks → progressive heel lift in CAM boot with WBAT, gradual neutral over 6-8 weeks, PT — comparable re-rupture rate vs surgery with proper protocol;

